collected to inform the economic analysis. An embedded process evaluation will 
obtain information to test out the theory of change underpinning the 
intervention and its acceptability to staff and residents.
DISCUSSION: This feasibility trial with embedded process evaluation and 
collection of health economic data will allow us to undertake detailed 
feasibility work to inform a future large-scale trial. It will provide valuable 
information to inform research procedures in this important but challenging 
area.
TRIAL REGISTRATION: ISRCTN registry, ISRCTN16076575 . Registered on 25 June 
2015.

